data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE Saturday, December 16 from 1:00-4:00 PM***Welcome to 518 Idamarie! This charming two-story home boasts four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, offering a comfortable and spacious living experience. Nestled in Converse, Texas, it provides a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of San Antonio while maintaining convenient access to the city. As you step inside, you'll discover a well-appointed interior with ample room for all your needs. The main floor features a generous living room, a chef's kitchen ready for culinary adventures, and a cozy breakfast nook. The primary bedroom with en suite is also located on the main level.  Upstairs, a large loft area and three additional bedrooms add versatility to the living space. Outside, the expansive backyard backs up to a serene greenbelt, enhancing your privacy and providing a tranquil backdrop for outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful home your own, offering the perfect balance of suburban peace and city accessibility.
